  "description": "<i>Tiles</i> is a <i><a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/game/amiga/shanghai\">Shanghai</a></i> clone (according to the author, it is based on <i><a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/search/quick?game=GunShy\">GunShy</a></i> for the Mac). You must eliminate all tiles on the screen by marking pairs, but only tiles which are free to the left or right can be marked. Unlike other <i>Shanghai</i> variants, the tiles are not traditional mahjongg tiles, but pictogrammes resembling computer icons. The program is totally multitasking-friendly and comes with source code in TDI Modula-2.",
